Here is special web application that provide Google AMP standard compatibility for Simtech CS-CART e-commerce platform. 
Both application working under PHP 7.2 and now in DEV stage. 
Who is this work?

Theare two application now saving here: 
- CS-CART Plugin that provide modification on the CS-CART site, and add special changes in head on HTML <head> section at the cs-cart, 
that add <amphtml link> tag with link to second application, writing on Yii2 framework (advanced patterd improved by 
good knowning Yii developer - Kartik/Kraji)

Both application interoperate via REST API based on cs-cart server side.

To be continiue....
